**Innovation Strategy, Funding, Implementation **

I’m an innovation strategist and founder of **Braintomic**, an innovation group that fuses human expertise with machine-driven intelligence. 
I help organizations turn ideas into scalable outcomes — from securing multi-million-pound funding for advanced technologies to automating operations and strengthening digital defenses against evolving threats.

Over the last decade, I’ve guided projects across AI-driven diagnostics, robotics, blockchain, biotech (CRISPR, multiomic sequencing), and green energy platforms — supporting them from concept to commercialization.

I hold an **MBA** and an **MPharmS**, alongside certifications in **AI**, **Machine Learning**, and **Sustainability Standards**.

